subject: Basketball
College Athletics
NCAA Basketball Tournament (Men)
lead_paragraph: Cal Poly Pomona won its first N.C.A.A.  Division II men’s championship with a 65-53 victory over Indiana (Pa.) on Saturday in Springfield, Mass.
